~FT--==--==--==->-==--==--==-<-==--==--==--==--==--==-<-==--==--==->-==--==--==--
~FYCommand Name~CB:~RS think
~FT--==--==--==->-==--==--==-<-==--==--==--==--==--==-<-==--==--==->-==--==--==--
Command Usage: .think [your thoughts]
  
Synopsis:
  Allows a user to put their message into thought bubbles, to let everyone
  in the room that they are in, know what their thoughts are.
~FT--==--==--==->-==--==--==-<-==--==--==--==--==--==-<-==--==--==->-==--==--==--

